    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Genre of architectural drawings, prints, or designs in other media that suggest an unlikely or impossible arrangement and projected environment that is surprising to the viewer.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
